WEBVTT

00:10.460 --> 00:11.530
<i> PREVIOUSLY ON "QUEEN SUGAR"...</i>

00:11.530 --> 00:14.660
MY BABY'S
GOING TO HARVARD!

00:14.660 --> 00:15.760
ALRIGHT, NOW!

00:15.760 --> 00:17.360
Nova: I LEARNED SOMETHING
ON MY BOOK TOUR

00:17.360 --> 00:18.460
THAT I THINK
YOU SHOULD KNOW.

00:18.460 --> 00:21.330
JUST IN CASE YOU NEED MORE...
AMMUNITION.

00:21.330 --> 00:24.730
-CHARLEY, I KNOW WHO I AM.
-DO YOU? REALLY?

00:24.730 --> 00:26.190
TURN ON THE NEWS.

00:26.200 --> 00:28.030
<i> I'VE LEARNED MY</i>
<i> GREAT-GRANDMOTHER LANDRY</i>

00:28.030 --> 00:31.790
<i> WAS A PROUD</i>
<i> AFRICAN-AMERICAN WOMAN.</i>

00:31.800 --> 00:35.090
THINK YOU CAN EVER THINK
ABOUT US AGAIN?

00:35.100 --> 00:37.230
I AIN'T BEEN ALL THE WAY
HONEST WITH YOU, DEESHA.

00:37.230 --> 00:39.990
I'M STILL IN LOVE
WITH DARLA.

00:40.000 --> 00:42.730
♪♪

00:42.730 --> 00:45.930
-BLUE.
-YES, POPS?

00:45.930 --> 00:49.390
HOW WE SUPPOSED TO BE
SPRING CLEANING

00:49.400 --> 00:52.190
WITHOUT
CLEANING SUPPLIES?

00:52.200 --> 00:53.790
OKAY.

00:53.800 --> 00:57.630
UM, I'LL GO GET THE PLASTIC
BAGS FROM THE KITCHEN.

00:57.630 --> 01:00.530
HEY. LOVE YOU.

01:00.530 --> 01:02.390
LOVE YOU, TOO.

01:02.400 --> 01:05.390
HURRY IT UP.

01:05.400 --> 01:07.260
[ SIGHS ]
THIS PLACE IS A MESS.

01:07.260 --> 01:09.460
♪ BORDERLINE CRAZY,
THOUGHTS TRYIN' TO BREAK ME ♪

01:09.460 --> 01:12.290
♪ BUT I WON'T ♪

01:12.300 --> 01:15.090
♪ QUIT COMPLAINING
WHEN YOU LIVIN'... ♪

01:15.100 --> 01:17.430
♪ YOUR CHOICE, YOUR VOICE,
YOU COULD STAND BACK ♪

01:17.430 --> 01:19.930
♪ OR COULD SPEAK YOUR DREAM
INTO REALITY ♪

01:19.930 --> 01:22.590
♪ THE WHISPERING HEART
BECOMES SCREAMS... ♪

